  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This unit of assurance documents the simulation credibility evidence for a CFD model predicting hemolysis in the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. The model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support worst-case operating condition identification for Class II cardiopulmonary bypass devices. A full 13-factor ASME V&V 40 assessment was conducted at Model Risk Level 2, with 7 factors formally assessed and 6 scoped out as acceptable at MRL 2. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; structured context-of-use metadata is not included in this submission tier.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-worst-case-hemolysis",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-cbp-cfd-hemolysis-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-cbp-experimental-hemolysis-benchmark",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/morrison-cbp-cfd-simulation-outputs-2024"
  ],
